Package: knitcitations
Type: Package
Title: Citations for knitr markdown files
Authors@R: person("Carl", "Boettiger", role=c("aut", "cre"),
    email="cboettig@gmail.com")
Version: 1.0.4
Description: knitcitations provides the ability to create dynamic
    citations in which the bibliographic information is pulled from the
    web rather than having to be entered into a local database such as
    bibtex ahead of time. Knitcitations is primarily aimed at authoring
    in the R markdown format, and can provide outputs for web-based
    authoring such as linked text and tooltips over inline citations.
    Cite using a DOI, URL, or bibtex file key.  See the package URL for
    details.
URL: https://github.com/cboettig/knitcitations
License: MIT
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: R (>= 3.0), methods
